 *
 *   - GND  = EXIO D pin 3, 4, 7, 8, 12, 17, 18
 *   - CS#  = EXIO D pin 27
 *   - SCK  = EXIO D pin 25
 *   - MOSI = EXIO D pin 21
 *   - MISO = EXIO D pin 23
